_sText:
An update of gg_Accumulator.

Fixes:
-More Decals
-MUCH less props, and no phsyics props
-Deleted office crates as they did not fit the theme
-Fixed a minor brush overlay at doors at spawn
-Added env_embers in roof light
-Added ambient sounds in some spots
-Small optimization increase
-FPS increased
   -At spawn around 50
   -Other places over 80

I had at LOWEST 49 at spawn, and at most other places I had over 100. Some places even reached over 170. Hope that's better for you guys.

I did not create brush crates as I wanted this to look more realistic, and brush crates would look out of place in this map.

Enjoy!
